snippet.title: Demonetisation: Meet Mumbai's First SBI Society Leading the Way to a Cashless India

localized.description:
Demonetisation: Here is the Mumbai's first SBI society which is leading the way to a cashless India. All residents, labours and shop owners are using buddy app of SBI for cashless payments.
